  <slide>
     <text xp="20" yp="80" sp="3">Deck is:</text>
     <text  xp="20" yp="70" sp="2" wp="50" font="serif" type="block">
     a Go package that enables clients to
     to use the same XML markup to produce presentations on a variety of media and formats.</text>
     <text xp="20" yp="40" sp="2" wp="50" font="serif" type="block">
     Deck elements are: text, list, image, line, rect, ellipse, arc, curve, and, 
     layout are object sizes are specified in percentages,
     resulting in scalable slides that adapt to any size or orientation.
     </text>
  </slide>

