  <slide>
     <text xp="20" yp="80" sp="3">Installing and running clients</text>
     <text xp="10" yp="60" sp="1.5" type="code">$ go get github.com/ajstarks/deck/vgdeck  # for the Raspberry Pi
$ go get github.com/ajstarks/deck/pdfdeck # to make PDF decks
$ vgdeck deck.xml                         # interactive session
$ pdfdeck deck.xml > deck.pdf             # make a PDF deck</text>
